---
title: Balsamic-Glazed Pork & Cucumber Salad with Tomato & Herby Mayonnaise
description: Get ready to savour the sweet and tangy goodness of tonight’s spectacular salad. A fresh, crisp salad is topped with balsamic-glazed pork, perfectly caramelised and juicy! Don’t forget the drizzle of herby mayo—it’s the creamy finishing touch that ties this delicious meal together!

